message:
[server] Improve repo size computation.

* Count file sizes instead of block sizes;
* Computer one repo size every second;
* Fix a memory bug.

[win] Fix a few bugs for server.

* evbuffer_write() doesn't work for file on Windows;
* bufferevent_new_socket() requires socket be non-blocking;
* Provide --disable-client config option on Windows;
* Remove --enable-httpserver config option, default when --enable-server is true.

[client] Fix two GC related bugs.

* Don't index worktree when GC is running;
* Save remote head id for normal download tasks too.

Fix bug when dir entry name is too long.

* truncate the name in memory when load it from disk;
* ignore file/dir with too long name in commit.

[client] Fix minor bugs in sync algorithm.

* Transition to error state when commit fails;
* In manual sync, start syncing even no files to be commited;
* Allows to add .git files.

Fix a few bugs on seafile server.

* Should use EVP_DecryptFinal_ex() in httpserver;
* Close unused fd for transfer.
